value:
Lord Manfroy's orders are...absolute.
I cannot abide those that oppose him.

Julius... Brother... Cover this world
in darkness... End...everything.

The arrival of the dark god, Lord
Loptous...is upon us... It cannot be
stopped...not by anyone...

The sacred text...Naga? I know it not!
Cease your...vile corruption...

Lord Seliph... Lewyn... My head...
It feels as if it's being split in two...

You must serve Loptous as well...
as $Nf does...
All will be as Lord Loptous wills it...

Soon...all will be...covered
in darkness...
So...cold... I cannot...move!

With this power...the world will
soon fall...to darkness...

I am...Julia, servant of the great
priest Lord Manfroy... Faithful
disciple of Lord Loptous...

When did the world...become such
a dark...and cold place...$k$pThere is only despair... Sadness
and pain...$k$pYou accept that? Here...in this world?$k$pThe solution...is destruction. Yet...
a strange voice echoes...through my
mind... A warm voice...$k$pSeliph... Seliph? Who...is Seliph?
And why does the name bring...
tears to my eyes...
ハアッ
Die...
アアッ…
You...!
Yes, Lord Manfroy...
Everyone will die.
Let the darkness come...
Impediment!
Lord Seliph, I remember…
Cackle...
I serve only the great priest... Lord Manfroy.
Hmm? Are you not terrified of me?
I will dispose of all who stand in Lord Manfroy's way.
There is no way to stop the darkness encroaching on this world.
The almighty dark god Loptous will be reborn!
Seliph... This is familiar, but whose is it? Saying it, I feel a strange warmth...
I'm sure you will join me in celebrating the resurrection of our god, Loptous...
You...
What...is it?
As you command.
